    {
      "id": "PopularPost149112",
      "post_content": "Yes, but those non-flyers are not riders, but ground support and thus your band can be blocked by non-flyers.  \n  \nNever understood what was the problem with banding. I just think that they couldn't get it right for computers. Banding had three rules:  \n  \n1. Only one non-banding per attack group.  \n2. Attacking group is blocked as one and can be blocked by any that can block one in the group.  \n3. Player who had banding creature attacking or blocking gets to distribute the incoming damage.  \n  \nIt was the 'band with others' that got the situation confusing.  \n  \nAll these creatures that give their P/T as +P/+T to attacking or blocking creature when tapped don't work like band. First of all banding is commitment that is done before blockers are announced when the bonus giving is normally done after. Secondly only with a bander gets the defender say how to distribute the damage.  \n  \nBut on the other hand, concerning this card: Evasion & banding don't mix very well.",
      "posted_by": "tavaritz",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost149112\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_post\">Yes, but those non-flyers are not riders, but ground support and thus your band can be blocked by non-flyers.<br/><br/>Never understood what was the problem with banding. I just think that they couldn't get it right for computers. Banding had three rules:<br/><br/>1. Only one non-banding per attack group.<br/>2. Attacking group is blocked as one and can be blocked by any that can block one in the group.<br/>3. Player who had banding creature attacking or blocking gets to distribute the incoming damage.<br/><br/>It was the 'band with others' that got the situation confusing.<br/><br/>All these creatures that give their P/T as +P/+T to attacking or blocking creature when tapped don't work like band. First of all banding is commitment that is done before blockers are announced when the bonus giving is normally done after. Secondly only with a bander gets the defender say how to distribute the damage.<br/><br/>But on the other hand, concerning this card: Evasion &amp; banding don't mix very well.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '149112'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy58371\">tavaritz</span>\r\n                                (7/10/2011 1:54:32 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"5.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/>\n<br/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    \u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>"
